        "text": "Maps a tech domain into an Obsidian vault: per-node deep-research (tiered + confidence-scored) → wikilinked .md notes under vault/<slug>/ → Precog + Polymarket odds attached, with draft-only Precog market proposals (await_approval, never signs). Aligns tightly with precog.market.",
